title: Baylor vs. Texas Tech score: Red Raiders' sweep of Bears allows Kansas to take control of Big 12 race - CBS Sports
content: Baylor vs. Texas Tech score: Red Raiders' sweep of Bears allows Kansas to take control of Big 12 race  CBS Sports
description: No. 11 Texas Tech finished a season sweep of No. 7 Baylor with an 83-73 win in Lubbock
